Name: GT Component
Description: It's a component present mainly or exclusively in a GT structure (including auxiliaries)
Rules:
Il campo aen4ProductLine del form aen4AdivDataForm deve essere valorizzato alternativamente con:
AENGasTurbine
AESGasTurbine; L'object type deve essere uno dei seguenti:
AENPartPRevision
AENGenericPRevision
AENMBOMPRevision
AENSBOMRevision
EntryRule: The field aen4ProductLine must be populated with 'AENGasTurbine' or 'AESGasTurbine'. If 'AENGasTurbine', the GT Model Rating must start with 'AE'. If 'AESGasTurbine', the GT Model Rating must start with 'GT'. Object Type must be one of the following: AENPartPRevision, AENGenericPRevision, AENMBill of Materials (BOM)PRevision, AENSBill of Materials (BOM)Revision.
AttributeValuationRule: GT Engine - Rating Model: If the Product Line starts with 'AEN', the 'GT Model Rating' value can be found in the 'Where Used' section or associated documents. If it starts with 'AES', the value will be 'GT'.
Validation Instrumented?: Check the validation documents to determine if the component is instrumented for validation purposes.
Standard Instrumented?: Refer to standard documentation to verify if the component is instrumented according to standard protocols.
